<h1>Cool Citrus Fire</h1>
<p class="note">A zesty <span class="highlight">post-hike booster</span> that blends citrus + frozen peppers for a potent, antioxidant-loaded refreshment.</p>
<h2 class="section-title">Ingredients</h2>
<ul>
<li>Juiced: 2 oranges (about 150ml)</li>
<li>Juiced: 1 medium carrot</li>
<li>Juiced: ½ cucumber</li>
<li>Juiced: small chunk of fresh ginger (or ¼ tsp powdered ginger)</li>
<li>Juiced: 1 small beetroot (vacuum-packed)</li>
<li>Blended: 100g frozen mixed peppers</li>
<li>Blended: 1 cube frozen spinach</li>
<li><em>Optional:</em> 1 tsp hemp protein powder or Applied Critical Greens powder</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="section-title">Instructions</h2>
<ul>
<li>Juice the oranges, carrot, cucumber, ginger, and beetroot.</li>
<li>Add the juice to your NutriBullet with the frozen peppers and spinach cube.</li>
<li>Add hemp or greens powder (if using).</li>
<li>Blend for 30 seconds until fully smooth and frothy.</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="section-title">Nutritional Highlights</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Calories:</strong> ~130 kcal</li>
<li><strong>Protein:</strong> 3g</li>
<li><strong>Carbohydrates:</strong> 27g</li>
